To install and run AlbumThing you'll need the following software packages:

 o Python <http://python.org/>
 o XMMS2 <http://xmms2.xmms.se/>
 o GTK+ <http://www.gtk.org/>
 o PyGTK <http://www.pygtk.org/>


To install AlbumThing all you need to do is issuing the following command:

 python ./setup.py install


There's, however, no need to do a full installation if you just want to give
AlbumThing a try. Run the following command to start it from within this
directory:

 python ./albumthing.py
